{
  "stem": "5371.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We heard that story later on, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we heard they put him on a march from that German camp, prisoner-of-war camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were marching towards Lublin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on the way they shot-- there were 600 Jewish prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They shot 400, and 200 arrived in Biala Podlaska.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were working-- there was an airport there, and they were working at the airport.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what kind of work they did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But there was a camp, there, at the airport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They did some work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we knew that my brother was there in that town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- How did you find that out?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, mail was still going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got mail, you know, from people who remained in-- see, we to-- we didn't stay too long there, because my older brother after a few days went right back to Mlawa.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He smuggled back, because they was-- from there, to go back to Mlawa, we had-- we had to cross a river, because Germany divided Poland into the Third Reich and part of the-- of the Polish government, which is the Polish-- they call it Gubernia Polska, which is like a puppet state.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my brother after a few days went right back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my mother and my two sisters and myself and my younger brother went to the neighboring town where my brother was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he provided for us a place to stay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed in somebody else's apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got a room in somebody else's apartment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were there for about three or four weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother decided I should-- my two sisters and myself should go back to Mlawa, because my-- my older brother, which was there back already, wrote us a card that we can come back.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
